OL,3,CFormer Conservative MP for Wrexham
OL,4,Cdefects to Reform
OL,6,FFormer defence minister Sarah Atherton
OL,7,Fhas announced she has defected to
OL,8,FReform UK after stepping away from the
OL,9,FConservative party.
OL,11,FMs Atherton, who previously served as
OL,12,Fa Member of Parliament for Wrexham,
OL,13,Flost her seat in the 2024 general
OL,14,Felection.
OL,16,FIn August of this year she announced
OL,17,Fshe was quitting the Conservative
OL,18,Fparty citing that it no longer aligned
OL,19,Fwith her values.
